<section id="how-to-play" aria-labelledby="how-to-play-title">
  <h2 id="how-to-play-title">How to Play</h2>

  <p>
    Borderline shows you the outline of a country or territory.
    Your task is simple:
    <strong>recognise it and name it</strong>.
  </p>

  <p>
    There are no flags.
    No capitals.
    No multiple choice.
  </p>

  <p>
    Type your answer and submit.
    Guess again if you’re wrong.
    The game keeps score.
  </p>

  <p>
    Speed matters.
    Accuracy matters.
    The timer is not on your side.
  </p>
</section>

